  "description": "A large container ship, identified as the \"Pasha Hawaii\", is docked at a port, surrounded by calm water with slight ripples. The ship is heavily loaded with colorful shipping containers stacked high on its deck. Several large, white port cranes are visible in the background, actively involved in loading or unloading cargo. The ship's superstructure is a mix of white and darker colors, and the overall scene is bathed in bright daylight under a clear blue sky. A smaller ship with 'CMA CGM' written on its side is also partially visible. The image evokes a sense of global trade and maritime activity.",
